Some people are complainy about mostly songs in Punjabi.
Agree with some point and with some not 

 1- This seson artist started with 2 represtation ( Sindhi/Pushto ) 

2- Most artists picked are emerging artist who made their name with their music.
( Mostly belongs from Punjab mannu , Annural , zeeshan hannan ) 

3- Its risky to put money and expect hit or views from unknown artist 
( Like people want songs in other languages ) 

4- Yes Artists From different regions should given opportunities.

5- Most of The Artists came from Punjab and karachi.
But artists from karachi were not picked .

snippet.textDisplay:
Almost 80 languages spoken in Pak. CS main theme was about to explore the diverse music of country but sorry to say about the commercial vibe i felt about this season. Bringing too much rap,  most songs in Punjabi, no new experimentation other than choreography and set design. 
Well xulfi bhai had created some magics in last season, so waiting for some magic in remaining songs of CS 15.
